Classes:
Logical Volumes:
- HAS TO HAVE A VOLUME GROUP

Volume groups:
-extends PV class
-

Physical Volume:
-@param String name

Constructor(s):
@param String name (sets the hard drive name)
@param PVName (extension from PHD class)
@param int giga (extension from PHD class)
@param PHD object


API(s):
generateUUID()
- generates a UUID whenever a PV is created
- Initialized in the constructor
- is added to a 2D array with the name of the name of the PV and the UUID

- getterMethod for name and 2D array

Physical Hard-drives:
-@param String name
-@param int gb (gigabits)

API(s):
- getter method for name
- getter method for gb